Class ColorFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.image.ImageFilter
      • iiv.filter.ColorFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ImageConsumer, Cloneable

    public class ColorFilter
extends ImageFilter
    ColorFilter sits between an ImageProducer and ImageConsumer replacing the color model of the data.
    Since:
    iiV1.0
